  <summary date="2021-08-20T18:16:03Z" status="Introduced in House">Eliminate Lavish Incentives To Electric Vehicles Act or the ELITE Vehicles Act

This bill terminates the tax credit for new qualified plug-in electric drive motor vehicles 30 days after this bill's enactment date. The credit is permanently repealed for taxable years beginning 1 year and 30 days after enactment.</summary>
